{"tid":1442553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[口號]警黑合作 流氓政權","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:02:22.000Z","uid":244509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7bba1213281d3e8c3bc4b4aa40a9078785687f","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"警黑合作 流氓政權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fda4fbc22d3fe757ac560e49c4cb0c6b819103","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64ef3f09847d99bb183691b6db6f0a4c3d16d760","tid":1442553,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjQ517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjQ517.jpg&h=8be1ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【求置頂】我係811港島東集會搞手，請大家冇野做就黎維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(冇人講)今日去深水埗!!!!唔好上淘寶！推爆我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19</a><br />\n<br />\n[求今日置頂] 811港島東要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[811] 深水埗 港島東 機場和你飛final call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c2811a1040dbce0bddcc2802648dbe5eeab352d8","tid":1442553,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n警黑合作 <br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n民建聯 工聯會 經民聯 無表態支持<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e6ab577363bf9c61be03b91bf88f3f967a9ad47","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca63a35bd2f5b43f0d78c9de3a5c4f4a6a09a8f2","tid":1442553,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3b20a8747eb4dbc310868dff81547d557198b3d3","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"247a35bfb60c8a4d236bc8db37e543d02648f2ab","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d2a48ed8bbeed2890321ffb98edb8f2292e59a5","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a8795dc04cf13e177cff81355d9bbaa44e1edb4","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a739c1b7382059002c8bc1b4723c5fb7ed4d39df","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2afdda1e03f63bed19e336eea34a32f5b11067c1","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4848fa62054ce9b768470af128e632e8aab24d1","tid":1442553,"uid":163938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"#721ThanksDAB"},{"pid":"615f0a528e3ca143cf75580726b14cfce8d4f9f8","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd1d5734cfa1543a209ca71bb0478a0d234a5fb2","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f914a07d47f268ea4d014c6717b2158cc2d7f124","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ee855332eb14c7920686732f59b1de2875c8a2d","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e7a96892565dd016758842344da7c168dfe9e7f","tid":1442553,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">社會垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"5739f48c4b1d3e12d1e4376d61e92a998eb29a1e","tid":1442553,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=918f75e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">46,460</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 13:07）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"206177abccdba1f0c089be9017432c7ee03423de","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c60f979ff87aa17aa9e7df4d5b4cd267654ac817","tid":1442553,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7bba1213281d3e8c3bc4b4aa40a9078785687f","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"警黑合作 流氓政權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"小心誤變成連登蠕蟲及幫兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dAEcdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dAEcdS</a><br />\n幫推  光復連登<br />\n<br />\n有D繞口<br />\n警黑同盟，出賣港人／禍國殃民"},{"pid":"9495ced047433295ca8e77cc032fe400463ffb80","tid":1442553,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60f979ff87aa17aa9e7df4d5b4cd267654a